<div class="intro">
    <p>
        Welcome to the {{ REPONAME }} hosted Mod Repository for Summoner : Modloader for Scrolls.
	Here you will find an overview of the available mods in this repository, with their 
	functionality and requirements. Installing mods from this repository is done in-game.
	Add this repository to Summoner by adding the following url in-game: 
    </p>
	<code>{{ REPOURL }}</code>
    <p>
	Summoner : Modloader for Scrolls can be downloaded from the <a href="http://www.scrollsguide.com/summoner">Summoner page on Scrollsguide</a>.
